Word count - count the amount of lines, words, or characters

ie:

wc textdoc.txt

extras here:

wc -l textdoc.txt     #just the line count please
wc -m textdoc.txt     #just the amount of characters please
wc -w textdoc.txt     #just the amount of actual words please

wc -l -w textdoc.txt  #just the amount of lines and also actual words please

etc
